Text:
Hi Steve, Juliana Martell is my neighbor who recommended you when I asked her for plumber recommendations. She spoke very highly of you.

I live at 246 N 3rd St and would to see if I can schedule you asap. I just left you a voicemail as well.
Probably closer to 3.  But I will be there today
Actually just let me know when your ready    I’m right next door
There are a couple electricians here but that shouldn’t get in your way
Okay. Walking up now. About 5 min
Ok I’ll meet you out front
The building association is aiming for Monday from Noon-2pm and they are confirming with me tomorrow
We will let you know when it’s 100 percent confirmed

Correction: the building just called back. They are turning off the water this Friday, from noon - 2pm or until you’re done. NOT Monday. This Friday. Can you confirm that works for you and you’ll be here at noon?
Hey. As far as tomorrow goes.  Do you have parking available?
Call when here and I’ll get you in
Just gotta run to the supply house.  Will be there right at 12
Water is getting shut off for building now
Hi Steve, please share invoice and plumber report and I’ll pay asap
Hey. Yes. I’ll get that over tonight.  Sorry for the delay
Can you send me your address and apartment number

Sent that over last night


You can Venmo or send me a check.  Doesn’t matter to me
No problem.  Let me know if you need me for anything else
I referred you to my mother-in-law she lives in Center City around Rittenhouse I figured you’d love a referral so she would be a good one in case she reached out
Her name is Mary and I think she’s going to call you soon
